Class CustomRunnable

  • java.lang.Object
    • backend.server.CustomRunnable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LoginRunnable, StudentRunnable

    public abstract class CustomRunnable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Base class for all runnables in project backend. Handles socket I/O and Threading.
    Author:
    Devon Vipond, Robyn Scholz, Janam Marthak
